Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.82,0:41:19.41,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Always give my love to you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.70,0:41:21.54,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Always give my love
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.00,0:41:24.66,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Always give my love to you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.79,0:41:32.84,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}son janai!? ima kara demo\Niin janai!? yareru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.79,0:41:32.84,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Don't you think so!? From now on, let's... Isn't it great!? Do what we can
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.93,0:41:43.52,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}omotta doori ni yatte miyou\Nkimi to deau made
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.93,0:41:43.52,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}With the way I feel now, I know I had nothing before you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.02,0:41:50.19,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}nani mo nakatta keredo me wo tojite omou
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.02,0:41:50.19,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}But when I close my eyes and think...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.32,0:41:54.90,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}issho ni ikiru basho ga aru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.32,0:41:54.90,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}I know there's a place where we can live together
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.11,0:42:01.41,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}always ai wo mune ni yuuki wo dashite
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.11,0:42:01.41,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}There will always be love in my heart, I've built up courage
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.66,0:42:06.00,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}tatoe sore ga dame da to shite mo ne
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.66,0:42:06.00,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}To say something is impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.12,0:42:11.42,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}No sore dake ga jibun janai
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.12,0:42:11.42,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}No, that's not like me
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.55,0:42:16.97,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Yes kazamuki ga kawatta ima tobitatou
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.55,0:42:16.97,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Yes, the wind has changed, let's start now
