Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.26,0:42:21.64,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Always give my love to you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.68,0:42:22.47,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Always give my love
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.31,0:42:29.15,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Always give my love
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.70,0:42:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't believe I said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.28,0:42:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was really wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.99,0:42:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.00,0:42:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just figured Shinichi would've said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.96,0:42:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.08,0:42:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking fondly of your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.92,0:42:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.18,0:43:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Courage...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.39,0:43:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gives you the strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.60,0:43:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To do what's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.23,0:43:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Haibara Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.78,0:43:21.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.70,0:43:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pleasure is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.62,0:43:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you too.
